data.description: This charming two-story home is a perfect blend of comfort and style.   A well-thought-out design, it offers a welcoming atmosphere for you and your family.  The house boasts a classic exterior featuring a combination of brick and siding, creating a timeless and elegant look.   Upon entering, you step into a spacious foyer that opens up to the heart of the home. To the Right you'll find a cozy living room, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying quiet family evenings. To the right, there's a formal dining room with ample space for hosting dinner parties.  The real highlight of this home is the open-concept kitchen and family room area. The kitchen is flooded with natural light, thanks to large windows and a sliding glass door that leads to the expansive deck.   Onlooking your own private Apple Tree.  The Main bedroom features an en-suite bathroom  A half bathroom is located on the first floor for guest convenience.  The attached garage provides parking for two cars and additional storage space. Conveyed "As Is"
